| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-5178 — Recovery Inhibition (dispossessor)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 493a4489-2b25-58d5-87d4-1bb2203f0ae1"
